  KEY INSIGHT: The paper computes Z3/Z1 as PROPORTION ratio (z3%/z1%),
  normalizing by total mutations per zone. When all cancers are pooled,
  the Z3 enrichment affects ALL classes (because Z3 has more mutations
  universally). Only within BRCA, C>T is the specifically enriched class.
  The validation test was using raw count ratio instead of proportion ratio.

